import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react";
import { useFonts } from 'expo-font';
import axios from 'axios';
import { StatusBar } from 'expo-status-bar';
import { View, Text, Alert } from 'react-native';
import { Container, Content, BackContainer, BackContent, TopContainer, SearchInput, 
  ContainerSearch, Filter, DataContent, DataLab, DataReplyLab, DataLimiter, IconsContent, IconContent } from "./styles/StylePrice";
import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-native-fontawesome'
import { faRightFromBracket, faHouse, faArrowUpAZ, faMagnifyingGlass, faEllipsisVertical, faPen, faEye, faTrashCan } from "@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons";
import { Menu, MenuProvider, MenuOptions, MenuOption, MenuTrigger } from 'react-native-popup-menu';


function Preco({ navigation }) {

  const confirm = () =>
  Alert.alert(
    "Está certo disso?",
    "Você está a um passo de excluir esse registro.",
    [
      { text: "Sim, prosseguir", onPress: () => console.log("Sim") },
      { text: "Não, voltar", onPress: () => console.log("Não") }
    ]
  );

    return (
        <Container>
          <StatusBar backgroundColor="#677689"/>         
          <TopContainer>
                 <ContainerSearch>
                <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faMagnifyingGlass} size={ 25 } color={ '#677689' }/>
                </ContainerSearch>                       
             <SearchInput/>
                <Filter>                               
                <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faArrowUpAZ}  size={ 25 } color={ '#677689' }/>
                </Filter>                               
          </TopContainer>

          <Content contentContainerStyle={{alignItems: 'center' }}>
              <DataContent>
                <DataLimiter>
                <DataLab> Produto: <DataReplyLab> Ração GranPlus Choice Frango e Carne para Cães Adulto s - 15kg</DataReplyLab> </DataLab>               
                <DataLab> Codigo: <DataReplyLab> 00032 </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
                <DataLab> Unidade: <DataReplyLab> 1 </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>               
                </DataLimiter>
                <IconsContent>
                  <IconContent>
                  <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faPen} size={ 15 } color={ '#dbdbdb' }/>               
                  </IconContent>
                  <IconContent>
                  <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faEye} size={ 15 } color={ '#dbdbdb' }/>  
                  </IconContent>
                  <IconContent onPress={confirm}>
                  <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faTrashCan} size={ 15 } color={ '#dbdbdb' }/> 
                  </IconContent>
                </IconsContent>
              </DataContent>

              <DataContent>
              <DataLimiter>
                <DataLab> Produto: <DataReplyLab> Ração Úmida GranPlus Gourmet Sachê para Cães Adultos Sabor Ovelha - 100g </DataReplyLab></DataLab>
                <DataLab> Codigo: <DataReplyLab> 00098 </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
                <DataLab> Unidade: <DataReplyLab> 1 </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
                </DataLimiter>            
                <IconsContent>
                  <IconContent onPress={confirm}>
                  <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faPen} size={ 15 } color={ '#dbdbdb' }/>               
                  </IconContent>
                  <IconContent>
                  <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faEye} size={ 15 } color={ '#dbdbdb' }/>  
                  </IconContent>
                  <IconContent onPress={confirm}>
                  <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faTrashCan} size={ 15 } color={ '#dbdbdb' }/> 
                  </IconContent>
                </IconsContent>      
              </DataContent>
              
              <DataContent>
              <DataLimiter>
                <DataLab> Produto: <DataReplyLab> Ração Úmida Hills Prescription Diet A/D Cuidados Críticos para Cães e Gatos - 156g </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>             
                <DataLab> Codigo: <DataReplyLab> 00076 </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
                <DataLab> Unidade: <DataReplyLab> 1 </DataReplyLab> </DataLab>
                </DataLimiter>
                <IconsContent>
                  <IconContent>
                  <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faPen} size={ 15 } color={ '#dbdbdb' }/>               
                  </IconContent>
                  <IconContent>
                  <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faEye} size={ 15 } color={ '#dbdbdb' }/>  
                  </IconContent>
                  <IconContent onPress={confirm}>
                  <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faTrashCan} size={ 15 } color={ '#dbdbdb' }/> 
                  </IconContent>
                </IconsContent>  
              </DataContent>

          </Content>

          <BackContainer>
            <BackContent onPress={() => navigation.navigate('Home')}>             
            <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faHouse} size={ 52 } color={ '#677689' }/>
            </BackContent>
            <BackContent onPress={() => navigation.navigate('Login')}>             
            <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faRightFromBracket} size={ 52 } color={ '#677689' }/>
            </BackContent>
          </BackContainer>
        </Container>
    );
  };

  export default Preco;
